timeline.bodyText:
NOT_IMPLEMENTED is "Feature not implemented: {0}.", so requires a parameter.
e.g.
throw StandardException.newException(SQLState.NOT_IMPLEMENTED, dataValue.getClass().getSimpleName() + " can't be used in mapToTxId" );

