replies.bodyText:
Thanks Martin for the nice catch!
I changed it, and now we get a better error message:
splice> select * from t1 as of time('12:11:11');
ERROR 0A000: Feature not implemented: SQLTime can not be used with time travel query.
splice> select * from t1 as of 3.4;
ERROR 0A000: Feature not implemented: SQLDecimal can not be used with time travel query.
